    "title": "Tapping for always behind",
    "subtitle": "A tapping practice for the chronic catching-up feeling",
    "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice for the always-behind feeling: the low-grade sense that there is a correct pace you are failing to meet. The script targets the belief that the schedule exists somewhere and you are late to it.",
    "sourceNotes": "EFT (Emotional Freedom Technique) developed by Gary Craig (1990s). Script and framing original to homemade.education.",
    "body": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the always-behind feeling. Not a specific overdue task. The structural state of feeling like you are perpetually failing to keep up with a pace that exists somewhere. Set by someone. And that you have not yet reached.",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "how EFT tapping works",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "link",
                  "attrs": {
                    "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": " first.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The practice",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Karate chop",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even though I feel behind, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even though I don't know behind whose schedule I'm behind, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even though the catching-up feeling never fully clears. I am open to the possibility that I am not actually late.",
                      "type": "text",
                      "marks": []
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Tapping round",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Eyebrow:** This behind feeling.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Side of eye:** There is a correct pace I am not meeting.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under eye:** I don't know who set it.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under nose:** I have been catching up for years.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Chin:** The finish line keeps moving.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Collarbone:** What if there is no correct pace?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under arm:** What if behind is a feeling, not a fact?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Top of head:** I am allowed to question the schedule.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Reframe to positive",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Eyebrow:** I am moving at my actual pace.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Side of eye:** That is the only pace available to me.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under eye:** Things are getting done.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under nose:** Not everything at once.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Chin:** That is true for everyone.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Collarbone:** I can put the behind feeling down.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under arm:** I am not late to my own life.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Top of head:** Right now I am exactly where I am.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Where this practice comes from",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
